    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo defines a portion of the Management Information Base (MIB) for use with network management protocols in TCP/IP based internets.  In particular it defines objects for managing a client of the Common Open Policy Service (COPS) protocol. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
